<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/images/witechlogo.png" type="image/png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/departmentform.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-B4gt1jrGC7Jh4AgTPSdUtOBvfO8shuf57BaghqFfPlYxofvL8/KUEfYiJOMMV+rV" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-9/reFTGAW83EW2RDu2S0VKaIzap3H66lZH81PoYlFhbGU+6BZp6G7niu735Sk7lN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Community Builder Specialist</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-12 volunteer-box">
<div class="back bg-dark px-5 py-3 fs-5" style="text-align: right;">
                    <a href="/outreach" style="color:rgb(253, 190, 71);">Go Back</a>
                  </div>
                        <div class="form-box"> 
                            <h2>Community Builder Specialist Form</h2>
                            <form action="#" onsubmit="submitForm('com-build-opr');return false;">
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="mName">Full Name</label>
                                    <input type="text" name="mName"  id="mName" placeholder="Name" class="form-control" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="mMail">E-Mail</label>
                                    <input type="email" name="mMail"  id="mMail" placeholder="E-mail" class="form-control" required>
                                </div>                            
                                
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="mContact">Contact</label>
                                    <input type="text" minlength="10" maxlength="10" name="mContact" id="mContact" placeholder="Contact" class="form-control" required>
                                </div>
                                
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="education">Educational Details(Name of college/university,degree,Academic year)</label>
                                    <textarea name="education" class="form-control" cols="20" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="cv">CV (Google Docs Link)</label>
                                    <input type="text" name="cv"  id="" placeholder="C.V Link" class="form-control" required>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="question1">What are the key strategies to boost a brand i.e., to increase engagement?</label>
                                    <textarea name="question1" class="form-control" cols="40" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="question2">What do you think makes a community strong?</label>
                                    <textarea name="question2" class="form-control" cols="40" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="question2">How will this job boost your career?</label>
                                    <textarea name="question2" class="form-control" cols="40" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <label for="question3"> 
                                        Task:A company mostly focuses on the demographics of a specific range, say 16-25 years of age. In the upcoming events, it plans to create workshops and seminars for the older age demographic. Hence it wants to widen the range of its demographics slowly to gain the appropriate audience for the upcoming events keeping in mind the speakers and mentors and other contributors. As a community builder, how will you increase the engagement to the desired demographics of up to and above 25 years. 
                                    </label>
                                       
                                    <textarea name="question3" class="form-control" cols="40" rows="4" required></textarea>
                                </div>

                                <div class="button-row">
                                    <button class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                                </div>
                                <div id="formalert"></div>
                            </form>

                        </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div> 
    <script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"></script> 
    <script src="/javascript/departmentform.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
